555
00:43:20.557 --> 00:43:23.310
<i>♪ I want him ♪</i>

556
00:43:23.393 --> 00:43:26.563
<i>♪ To know ♪</i>

557
00:43:29.900 --> 00:43:34.905
<i>♪ What I have done ♪</i>

558
00:43:39.368 --> 00:43:41.829
<i>♪ I want him ♪</i>

559
00:43:41.912 --> 00:43:44.373
<i>♪ To know ♪</i>

560
00:43:45.791 --> 00:43:48.669
