00:44:19.992 --> 00:44:21.785
Bagged me a white fucking buck!

567
00:44:22.536 --> 00:44:23.620
You see that. man?

568
00:44:23.704 --> 00:44:25.956
Holy shit. I almost tagged you. dude.

569
